">{{cite web|url=http://gizmodo.com/5025682/iphone-meet-star-wars-the-force-unleashed|title=iPhone, Meet Star Wars: The Force Unleashed|accessdate=2008-07-18|first=Mark|last=Wilson|date=2008-07-16|publisher=[[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]]|archive-date=2018-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012115502/https://gizmodo.com/5025682/iphone-meet-star-wars-the-force-unleashed|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[N-Gage|N-Gage]]<ref name="N-Gage version">、{{cite web |url=http://www.nokia.com/A4136001?newsid=1172728 |date=2007-12-03 |title=THQ Wireless, Lucasfilm Ltd., and LucasArts to bring Star Wars: The Force Unleashed(TM) to N-Gage |publisher=Nokia |accessdate=2007-12-04 |archive-date=2008-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080316110251/http://www.nokia.com/A4136001?newsid=1172728 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]<ref>{{citeweb|url=http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/starwars2007/index.html?q=Star%20Wars:%20The%20Force%20Unleashed|title=Star Wars: The Force Unleashed|accessdate=2008-01-28|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|archive-date=2007-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930220845/http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/starwars2007/index.html?q=Star%20Wars:%20The%20Force%20Unleashed|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]<ref name="lagamesbyplatform">{{cite web |url=http://www.lucasarts.com/games/platform.html |title=Games by Platform |publisher=[[LucasArts|LucasArts]] |accessdate=2008-03-08 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5v4Zuz15v?url=http://www.lucasarts.com/games/platform.html |archivedate=2010-12-18 }}</ref>和支持[[Java|Java]]的[[手機|手機]]<ref name="mobilejava">{{cite web|publisher=Pocket Gamer|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Mobile/Star+Wars:+The+Force+Unleashed+mobile/news.asp?c=8603|title=New screens for Star Wars: The Force Unleashed mobile game|first=Stuart|last=Dredge|accessdate=2008-08-27|date=2008-08-27|work=Mobile News|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809091211/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/Mobile/Star+Wars:+The+Force+Unleashed+mobile/news.asp?c=8603|dead-url=no}}</ref>所開發。本遊戲在[[北美|北美]]於2008年9月16日發售，在[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]與[[東南亞|東南亞]]於9月17日發售，在[[歐洲|歐洲]]於9月19日發售。<ref name="1.5M">{{Cite web|url=http://www.starwars.com/games/videogames/news20080923.html|title=The Force Unleashed Sells 1.5 Million Units Worldwide in Under One Week|date=2008-09-23|accessdate=2008-10-25|publisher=[[Lucasfilm|Lucasfilm]]|archive-date=2009-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090402030455/http://starwars.com/games/videogames/news20080923.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>PlayStation 3和Xbox 360版的[[試玩版|試玩版]]於8月21日提供下載，LucasArts還在12月5日為這兩個平臺提供了[[下載內容|一個下載關卡]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/xbox360/action/starwars2007/video/6196617/on-the-spot--08-21-08?tag=;title;1|title=On the Spot|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2008-08-21|accessdate=2008-08-22}}</ref><ref name="dlc1released">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/show_blog_entry.php?topic_id=26698514|title=Force Unleashed DLC now available|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2008-12-05|date=2008-12-05|author=TomM_GScom|archive-date=2008-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081208072204/http://www.gamespot.com/news/show_blog_entry.php?topic_id=26698514|dead-url=no}}</ref>

原力釋放計劃銜接了[[星球大戰|星球大戰]]的兩個三部曲并介紹了一位新主角、[[達斯·維德|達斯·維德]]的秘密學徒：[[弑星者|弑星者]]（Starkiller）。公眾對此作評價褒貶不一，表揚其令人信服的故事，強大的物理效果和令人印象深刻的藝術設計，但對其令人沮喪的遊戲性表示失望。儘管有著這些褒貶不一的評價，這款遊戲在[[美國|美國]]和澳大利亞都成為了暢銷作品，首月銷量超過100萬份。<ref name="NPD">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=20696|title=NPD: September Games Sales Down 6%, But Force, Fit, Rock Band 2 Reign|authorlink=Simon Carless|first=Simon|last=Carless|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=2008-10-16|accessdate=2008-11-06|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228193007/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=20696|dead-url=no}}</ref>

